bilingual.source: The bank offers competitive rates on mortgages.

bilingual.source: They gave us a very competitive direct quotation.
bilingual.target: 他们给了我们一个非常有竞争力的直接报价。

bilingual.source: The suppliers offer competitive prices for bulk orders.
bilingual.target: 供应商为大宗订单提供有竞争力的价格。

bilingual.source: The company offered a very competitive insurance contract.
bilingual.target: 这家公司提供了一个非常有竞争力的保险合同。

bilingual.source: The purveyor of office supplies offers competitive prices.
bilingual.target: 办公用品的供应商提供有竞争力的价格。

bilingual.source: The company offers competitive remuneration for its employees.
bilingual.target: 公司为员工提供有竞争力的报酬。

bilingual.source: The bank offers competitive interest rates on savings accounts.
bilingual.target: 该银行为储蓄账户提供有竞争力的利息费率。

bilingual.source: The employer offered a competitive salary to attract top talent.
bilingual.target: 这位雇主提供了有竞争力的薪水来吸引顶尖人才。

yingyinNormal.zh: 在竞争行为中，总有人要输。

yingyinNormal.en: Kite fighting? Oh, yeah. It's an extremely competitive, cutthroat sport.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斗风筝？对，一项极具竞争性和激烈性的运动。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you believe what a jerk Ross was being? Yeah, I know. He can get really competitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道罗斯那混蛋有多烂吗？我懂。他的好胜心最强了。

yingyinNormal.en: While providing competitive advantages in efficacy and safety. Now, this doesn't mean...
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时也在全力提升产品在功能性和安全性方面的竞争优势，然而，这并不代表...

yingyinNormal.en: I'm saying, if you were any other partner, I'd be as unhappy and competitive as I am now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是说，如果你是其他人，我会一样的好胜和不爽。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. In short, the merger of our two great companies will ensure our competitive edge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之，长话短说，我们两大公司的兼并将确保我们的竞争优势。

yingyinNormal.en: But actually there's truth in that. And the argument being that the content we've created just isn't as internationally competitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是还有一个事实，有人说我们创作的内容并没有要去竞争的意图。

yingyinNormal.en: Right, but all around the electrode, it's insulated so the electricity is directed into the steel. This furnace makes Nucor highly competitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的,在电极的周围它是绝缘的，电流直接进入钢铁。它提高了钢铁公司的竞争力。

yingyinNormal.en: And in a very competitive world, that really is a calling card, cause I can tell you as one who employs a lot of people, when I see Harvard, I sit a little bit straighter and say: Where if he or she? Bring them in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在这个充满竞争的世界，那的确是一张抢眼的名片。就我个人而言，我曾招聘过很多人，当我看到哈佛大学的字眼时，我总是会坐直一些，然后说：“他们在哪？把他们统统带过来。”

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 竞争优势；竞争力；竞技优势

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Our main challenge is that our national currency is rising, and we're losing <highlight>competitive</highlight> advantage to stone producers in India.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们面临的主要挑战是，我们的国家货币正在升值，我们正在失去与印度石材生产商竞争的优势。

examination_example.sentence: In the <highlight>competitive</highlight> game of biomedical science, research has been done on scientists who narrowly lost or won grant money.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在生物医学的竞争游戏中，研究的对象都是那些以微弱劣势输掉或赢得资助的科学家。
